tion%20in%20Milwaukee.%3Cp%3EWin%20McNamee%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20Thiel's%20first%20attempt%20to%20play%20kingmaker.%20The%20entrepreneur%20has%20always%20stood%20out%20as%20a%20conservative%20figure%20in%20the%20relatively%20left-leaning%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20but%20in%20recent%20years%20has%20become%20an%20increasingly%20dominant%20figure%20in%20the%20Republican%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Trump's%20biggest%20donors%20in%20the%202016%20presidential%20campaign%2C%20Thiel%20has%20re-emerged%20as%20a%20key%20player%20in%20the%20MAGA%20movement%20after%20largely%20sitting%20out%20the%202020%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20November%202023%2C%20he%20gave%20an%20interview%20to%20The%20Atlantic%20about%20his%20disappointment%20with%20Trump%20and%20announced%20he%20planned%20to%20cut%20off%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theatlantic.com%2Fpolitics%2Farchive%2F2023%2F11%2Fpeter-thiel-2024-election-politics-investing-life-views%2F675946%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERepublican%20politicians%20in%202024.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20reportedly%20donated%20more%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2022%2F02%2F14%2Ftechnology%2Frepublican-trump-peter-thiel.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2420%20million%20to%20support%2016%20Republican%20candidates%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20midterm%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThiel%20also%20appears%20to%20have%20pulled%20some%20of%20his%20Silicon%20Valley%20strings%20to%20advance%20Vance's%20campaign.%20He%20introduced%20Vance%20to%20David%20Sacks%2C%20a%20fellow%20PayPal%20Mafia%20colleague%2C%20who%20hosted%20a%20fundraiser%20for%20him%20and%20personally%20donated%20%241%20million%20to%20a%20pro-Vance%20Super%20PAC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2255eef3ed-dfea-4864-8563-6795001d6983%5C%22%3ESecret%20lobbying%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20in%20the%20tech%20world%20have%20been%20eagerly%20campaigning%20for%20Vance%20behind%20the%20scenes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.axios.com%2Fnewsletters%2Faxios-am-a57d5ac0-42e3-11ef-a18b-df9c93a5e649.html%3Futm_source%3Dnewsletter%26utm_medium%3Demail%26utm_campaign%3Dnewsletter_axiosam%26stream%3Dtop%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20Axios%20report%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20Musk%2C%20Sacks%2C%20and%20former%20Fox%20News%20presenter%20Tucker%20Carlson%20have%20been%20running%20a%20secret%20lobbying%20campaign%20for%20Vance%2C%20calling%20up%20Trump%20even%20after%20Saturday's%20assassination%20attempt%20to%20advocate%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Peter%20Thiel%20holding%20a%20microphone%20and%20sitting%20in%20a%20chair%20at%20the%20Cambridge%20University%20Union%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66966e8d5439fb59cebdb14a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPeter%20Thiel%20addressed%20the%20Cambridge%20University%20Union%20in%20Cambridge%2C%20England%20in%20May.%3Cp%3ENordin%20Catic%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThiel's%20formidable%20track%20record%20has%20extended%20beyond%20the%20political%20arena%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20outside%20investor%20in%20Facebook%2C%20Thiel%20bet%20on%20the%20company%20when%20no%20one%20else%20would%20%E2%80%94%20and%20is%20credited%20with%20transforming%20an%20up-and-coming%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20the%20slick%20CEO%20he%20now%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThiel%20was%20also%20a%20cofounder%20of%20PayPal%20and%20Palantir%20Technologies%20and%20made%20early%20investments%20in%20Airbnb%20and%20Spotify.%20His%20other%20success%20stories%20include%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeter-thiel-elon-musk-relationship-contrarian-