0line%20while%20sailing%20with%20my%20free-spirited%20son%2C%20who%20I%20thought%20might%20appreciate%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20first%20night%2C%20at%207%20p.m.%2C%20we%20found%20several%20lines%20leading%20into%20the%20main%20dining%20room.%20We%20were%20asked%20if%20we%20had%20a%20reservation.%20Puzzled%2C%20we%20explained%20that%20we%20didn't%20need%20one%20because%20we%20were%20doing%20flexible%20dining.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20directed%20to%20a%20different%20line%20for%20people%20without%20reservations.%20On%20the%20way%2C%20we%20passed%20the%20noticeably%20shorter%20line%20for%20passengers%20with%20assigned%20dining%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20waited%20about%2020%20minutes%20to%20be%20seated.%20After%20our%20meal%2C%20we%20made%20dinner%20reservations%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221bd0b3c8-342d-46d2-8200-bebf9a05660d%5C%22%3EFlexible%20dining%20can%20make%20it%20difficult%20to%20build%20new%20connections%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221877%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Toasting%20wine%20glasses%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66903f9d9caa6ed01e00eae2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221252%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESitting%20with%20strangers%20and%20committing%20to%20a%20mealtime%20might%20sound%20intense%2C%20but%20you%20might%20make%20a%20new%20friend.%3Cp%3EPixelsEffect%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20partaking%20in%20freestyle%20dining%20on%20the%20Norwegian%20Wind%2C%20my%20late%20wife%20and%20I%20asked%20to%20be%20seated%20with%20other%20people%20every%20night%20so%20we%20could%20see%20some%20fresh%20faces.%20But%20that%20never%20ended%20up%20happening%3A%20In%20our%20eight%20days%2C%20we%20ate%20only%20with%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20I%20loved%20having%20dinner%20with%20my%20wife%2C%20we%20did%20so%20every%20night%20at%20home.%20At%20sea%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20exp