0people%20thought%20we%20were%20intentionally%20doing%20something%20evil%2C%20which%20concerned%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20didn't%20do%20it%20to%20antagonize%20anyone%3B%20we%20did%20it%20to%20embrace%20the%20airport's%20personality%2C%20but%20I%20underestimated%20how%20strongly%20people%20believe%20in%20all%20of%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22434c828f-dda5-4f2c-9195-fa18ef871d1e%5C%22%3EThe%20tunnels%20aren't%20secret%20and%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20supernatural%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20Denver%20airport%20tour%20was%20sparked%20by%20the%20viral%20TikTok.%20It%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20just%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflying-ultra-low-cost-airlines-spirit-frontier-not-worth-it-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFrontier%20Airlines'%20ground-loading%20gates%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20people%20walk%20out%20to%20the%20plane%20via%20the%20tarmac%2C%20not%20jetbridges.%20Stegman%20said%20they%20simply%20weren't%20operating%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223133%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20ground-loading%20gates%20at%20Denver%20with%20people%20sitting%20and%20waiting.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6695867d5439fb59cebd8cca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222350%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStegman%20said%20the%20TikTok%20video%20was%20of%20the%20ground-loading%20gates%2C%20which%20are%20now%20operational%20and%20not%20spookily%20empty.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20not%20the%20only%20%26quot%3Bhidden%26quot%3B%20place%20in%20Denver%20Airport%20where%20theorists%20believe%20something%20nefarious%20is%20going%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20airport%20was%20constructed%2C%20few%20aerial%20photos%20of%20the%20project%20existed%2C%20and%20the%20ones%20that%20did%20exist%20showed%20a%20labyrinth%20of%20underground%20