%3EThe%20toe%20box%20and%20upper%20design%20might%20not%20be%20a%20good%20fit%20for%20people%20with%20decidedly%20narrow%20or%20wide%20feet%2C%20and%20the%20knit%20upper%20might%20not%20be%20durable%20enough%20for%20people%20who%20regularly%20blow%20out%20their%20sneakers.%20But%20the%20universal%20fit%20of%20these%20shoes%20means%20your%20feet%20will%20stay%20comfortable%2C%20even%20after%20walking%20long%20miles%20in%20them.%20And%20while%20they%20aren't%20cheap%2C%20you%20can%20snag%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-70725-20%26h%3Dc9b760985813069b61e5d8297ac65fec3ae6a5649c184e507f7264f1585a0877%26postID%3D669008866f84fbe6954112ff%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fstyle%252Fadidas-ultraboost-light-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fdp%252FB0C1LF23SP%253Fth%253D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAdidas%20Ultraboost%20Lights%20in%20select%20colorways%20for%20over%20half%20off%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0during%20Prime%20Day%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ECheck%20out%20our%20roundup%20of%20all%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fdeals%2Famazon-prime-day%5C%22%3Ebest%20Prime%20Day%20deals%20here%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20browse%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-70725-20%26h%3D34bc15ccce60d2d0302c5e05187d6e06b596c2043ec7a1cbf7763aa1cbe54721%26postID%3D669008866f84fbe6954112ff%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fstyle%252Fadidas-ultraboost-light-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fdeals%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon's%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fadidas-ultraboost-light-review%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721134233000%2C%22visual%22%3A%