ariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fjack-black-cancels-tenacious-d-tour-trump-assassination-joke-1236073486%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fjack-black-cancels-tenacious-d-tour-trump-assassination-joke-1236073486%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trainee%20IAS%20Officer%20Puja%20Khedkar%20Recalled%20To%20Academy%2C%20Training%20Put%20On%20Hold%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPuja%20Khedkar%2C%20a%20probationary%20IAS%20officer%20who%20is%20under%20scrutiny%20over%20alleged%20misuse%20of%20power%20and%20privileges%2C%20has%20been%20recalled%20to%20the%20Lal%20Bahadur%20Shastri%20National%20Academy%20of%20Administration%20in%20Mussoorie%20and%20her%20training%20put%20on%20hold.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20major%20action%20against%20Ms%20Khedkar%20who%20had%20been%20transferred%20to%20Washim%20from%20Pune%20(where%20she%20was%20originally%20posted)%20amid%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpuja-khedkar-row-explained-charges-against-trainee-ias-officer-her-family-6109493%5C%22%3Eallegations%20of%20manipulation%20of%20disability%20and%20OBC%20certificates%20%3C%2Fa%3Efor%20getting%20into%20the%20civil%20services.%20She%20has%20been%20recalled%20to%20the%20training%20academy%20for%20%26quot%3Bfurther%20necessary%20action%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20are%20hereby%20relieved%20from%20the%20District%20Training%20Programme%20of%20the%20State%20Government%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20release%20from%20the%20General%20Administration%20Department.%C2%A0She%20has%20been%20instructed%20to%20%26quot%3Bjoin%20the%20academy%20at%20the%20earliest%26quot%3B%20but%20not%20later%20than%20July%2023.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20academy%20trains%20civil%20servants%20of%20the%20IAS%20cadre%20and%20also%20conducts%20the%20foundation%20course%20of%20Group-A%20central%20civil%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20authenticity%20of%20various%20certificates%20submitted%20by%20her%20to%20the%20Union%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20(UPSC)%2C%20one%20of%20them%20indicating%20visual%20impairment%2C%20is%20being%20probed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Khedkar%20had%20earlier%20submitted%20two%20certificates%2C%20provided%20by%20the%20Ahmednagar%20District%20Civil%20Hospital%20in%202018%20and%202021%2C%20to%20the%20UPSC%20under%20the%20Persons%20with%20Benchmark%20Disabilities%20(PwBD)%20category.%20She%20was%2C%20however%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftrainee-ias-officer-puja-khedkar-news-puja-khedkar-fake-disability-certificate-aiims-puja-khedkar-medical-examination-6117453%5C%22%3Esent%20by%20the%20UPSC%20for%20a%20medical%20check-up%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Delhi's%20All%20India%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Science.%20She%2C%20however%2C%20skipped%20as%20many%20as%20six%20appointments%20between%20April%20and%20August%202022%2C%20claimed%20several%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20now%20emerged%20that%20she%20applied%20for%20a%20disability%20certificate%20from%20the%20Aundh%20government%20hospital%20in%20Pune%20in%20August%202022%2C%20but%20after%20medical%20tests%2C%20her%20application%20was%20rejected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202023-batch%20officer%20from%20Ahmednagar%20has%20alleged%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fproving-me-guilty-by-media-trial-wrong-trainee-ias-officer-puja-khedkar-6111570%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bmedia%20trial%26quot%3B%20against%20her%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20that%20she%20had%20been%20the%20victim%20of%20a%20misinformation%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20transferred%20from%20Pune%2C%20where%20she%20was%20posted%20as%20an%20assistant%20collector%2C%20to%20Washim%20as%20a%20supernumerary%20assistant%20collector%20after%20she%20was%20first%20accused%20of%20demanding%20perks%20and%20facilities%20to%20which%20she%20was%20not%20entitled%20as%20a%20trainee%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20alleged%20she%20