ccounts%2C%20which%20can%20be%20a%20powerful%20form%20way%20to%20reach%20a%20wide%20audience.%20Going%20viral%20also%20helped%20me%20to%20meet%20new%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20haven't%20graduated%20from%20high%20school%20yet%20and%20I%20started%20taking%20online%20classes%20instead%20a%20few%20months%20ago%20after%20I%20got%20suspended%20for%20taking%20meetings%20in%20the%20bathroom.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20then%20moved%20to%20San%20Francisco%20to%20work%20on%20building%20the%20company%20full-time.%20My%20parents%20are%20pretty%20chill%20about%20it%2C%20but%20for%20the%20first%20two%20months%2C%20they%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20little%20surprising%20for%20me%20to%20take%20a%20risk%20like%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20learned%20a%20ton%20and%20experienced%20some%20highs%20and%20lows.%20It's%20opened%20up%20my%20world%2C%20but%20it%20hasn't%20come%20without%20difficulty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20times%20when%20it's%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20what%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20I've%20figured%20it%20out%20along%20the%20way.%20Surrounding%20myself%20with%20experienced%20people%20like%20my%20cofounders%20and%20investors%20has%20been%20really%20helpful.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EGot%20a%20tech%20career%20story%20to%20share%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajmann%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Ejmann%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feric-zhu-aviato-tech-startup-raised-funds-high-school-bathroom-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721132350000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66964d855439fb59cebda927%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feric-zhu-aviato-tech-startup-raised-funds-high-school-bathroom-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Eric%20Zhu%2C%20now%2017%2C%20cofounded%20Aviato.%20He%20dropped%20out%20of%20high%20school%20and%20moved%20to%20San%20Francisco%20to%20run%20the%20startup%20full-time%20after%20raising%20%242.3%20million.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jmann%40insider.com%20(Jyoti%20Mann)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feric-zhu-aviato-tech-startup-raised-funds-high-school-bathroom-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Haryana%2C%20Amit%20Shah's%20Anti-Congress%20Warning%20On%20Muslim%20Reservation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHome%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20lashed%20out%20at%20the%20Congress%20Tuesday%2C%20accusing%20the%20party%20of%20having%20%26quot%3Bsnatched%20reservation%20from%20backward%20classes%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20giving%20it%20to%20Muslims%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah's%C2%A0%20comment%20was%20made%20in%20Haryana%2C%20which%20will%20hold%20an%20Assembly%20election%20later%20this%20year.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20Congress%20forms%20the%20government%2C%20they%20will%20do%20the%20same%20in%20Haryana%20too...%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20a%20Backward%20Classes%20Samman%20Sammelan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20Congress%20had%20always%20been%20against%20the%20backward%20classes%2C%20raking%20up%20a%20row%20-%20the%20issue%20of%20reservations%20to%20Muslims%20-%20that%20dominated%20headlines%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20all-out%20and%20fierce%20attack%20on%20his%20rival%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20referred%20to%20the%201957%20Kaka%20Kalelkar%20Commission%20report%20and%20pointed%20out%20the%20Congress%20had%20delayed%20implementing%20its%20recommendations.%20%26quot%3BIn%201980%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi%20shelved%20the%20Mandal%20Commission.%20When%20it%20was%20introduced%20in%201990%2C%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20opposed%20OBC%20reservation...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20declared%20that%20it%20was%20only%20in%202014%2C%20after%20Narendra%20Modi%20became%20Prime%20Minister%20for%20the%20first%20time%20that%20there%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bgovernment%20of%20Dalits%2C%20poor%2C%20and%20backward%20people%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20made%20reference%20to%20the%20fact%2027%20of%2071%20cabinet%20ministers%20are%20from%20backward%20classes.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20assure%20you%20we%20will%20not%20allow%20Muslim%20reservation%20in%20Haryana%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20the%20comment%20came%20in%20Haryana%20is%20seen%20as%20significant%2C%20since%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini%2C%20who%20replaced%20ML%20Khattar%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20ahead%20of%20the%20general%20election%2C%20is%20from%20the%20OBCs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20last%20month%20Mr%20Saini%20said%20reservation%20for%20backward%20classes%20in%20Group-A%20and%20Group-B%20government%20jobs%2C%20currently%20at%2015%20per%20cent%2C%20would%20be%20increased%20to%2027%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20he%20said%2C%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bin%20line%20with%20the%20central%20government's%20policy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20hit%20back%20strongly%2C%20directing%20Mr%20Shah%20to%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20is%20in%20power.%20The%20TDP%20is%20an%20ally%20of%20the%20BJP%3B%20its%2016%20Lok%20Sabha%20MPs%20are%20essential%20for%20Mr%20Modi%20to%20remain%20in%20power%20after%20the%20BJP's%20less%20than%20stellar%20poll%20result%2C%20in%20which%20it%20finished%2032%20seats%20of%20outright%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reference%20was%20to%20the%20TDP%20government's%20reservation%20policy%20for%20Muslims%2C%20who%20form%20a%20crucial%20vote%20bank%20in%20the%20state.%20Mr%20Naidu%20has%20offered%20no%20indication%20he%20will%20scrap%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20his%20son%20Nara%20Lokesh%20told%20NDTV%20last%20month%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20(reservation%20for%20Muslims)%20has%20been%20going%20around%20for%20the%20last%20two%20decades.%20We%20stand%20by%20it.%20We%20intend%20to%20continue%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20fact%20minorities%20continue%20to%20suffer%20and%20that%20they%20have%20the%20lowest%20per%20capita%20income.%20As%20a%20government%2C%20it%20is%20our%20responsibility%20to%20bring%20them%20out%20of%20poverty.%20So%20whatever%20decisions%20I%20take%20are%20not%20for%20appeasement%2C%20but%20to%20bring%20them%20out%20of%20poverty.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20election%20campaign%20the%20Muslim%20reservation%20issue%20was%20a%20major%20bone%20of%20contention%2C%20particularly%20after%20Mr%20Modi's%20comment%20in%20Rajasthan's%20Banswara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20plans%20in%20the%20Congress'%20manifesto%20for%20an%20%26quot%3Beconomic%20and%20institutional%20report%26quot%3B%20as%20part%20of%20a%20national%20caste%20survey%2C%20and%20to%20a%20remark%20by%20his%20predecessor%2C%20Dr%20Manmohan%20Singh%2C%20the%20PM%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BCongress%20says%20they%20will%20calculate%20gold%20with%20mothers%20and%20sisters...%20and%20distribute%20that%20property....%20that%20Muslims%20have%20first%20right%20on%20all%20resources...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remarks%20provoked%20an%20angry%20response%20from%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20accused%20Mr%20Modi%20of%20lying%20to%20divert%20voters'%20attention%20from%20genuine%20issues.%20The%20party%20pointed%20out%20its%20manifesto%20made%20no%20such%20claim%2C%20and%20Mr%20Gandhi%20explained%20the%20survey%20and%20its%20components%20were%20an%20%26quot%3Bimportant%20step%26quot%3B%20in%20understanding%20how%20sections%20of%20the%20society%20developed%20and%20what%20is%20needed%20to%20ensure%20equality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20also%20complained%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission.%20A%20notice%20was%20sent%20to%20BJP%20chief%20JP%20Nadda%20-%20and%20his%20Congress%20counterpart%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20after%20a%20complaint%20was%20filed%20against%20Mr%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmit%20Shah%20is%20on%20his%20second%20visit%20to%20poll-bound%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20was%20won%20by%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20then%20ally%2C%20former%20ex-Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Dushyant%20Chautala's%20JJP%20in%20the%20last%20election.%20It%20was%20swept%20by%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20two%20previous%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%3B%20the%20party%20won%20all%2010%20seats.%20But%20in%20the%202024%20poll%20the%20Congress%20made%20a%20strong%20comeback%2C%20winning%20five%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721132160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F5g5uq8j8_amit-shah_625x300_29_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharyana-assembly-election-muslim-reservation-amit-shah-in-haryana-amit-shahs-anti-congress-warning-on-muslim-reservation-6118666%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20lashed%20out%20at%20the%20Congress%20Tuesday%2C%20accusing%20the%20party%20of%20having%20%26quot%3Bsnatched%20reservation%20from%20backward%20classes%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20giving%20it%20to%20Muslims%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharyana-assembly-election-muslim-reservation-amit-shah-in-haryana-amit-shahs-anti-congress-warning-on-muslim-reservation-6118666%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharyana-assembly-election-muslim-reservation-amit-shah-in-haryana-amit-shahs-anti-congress-warning-on-muslim-reservation-6118666%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharyana-assembly-election-muslim-reservation-amit-shah-in-haryana-amit-shahs-anti-congress-warning-on-muslim-reservation-6118666%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Video%3A%20IAS%20Officer%20Puja%20Khedkar's%20Mother's%