C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20had%20earlier%20zeroed%20in%20on%20Hazaribagh%20as%20the%20origin%20place%20of%20the%20NEET-UG%20paper%20leak.%20The%20paper%20was%20leaked%20by%20Oasis%20school%20in%20Hazari%20Bagh%2C%20the%20CBI%20probe%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20that%20two%20sets%20of%20papers%20which%20reached%20there%20had%20their%20seals%20broken%20and%20instead%20of%20flagging%20the%20issue%20the%20staff%20of%20the%20school%20remained%20tight-lipped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNine%20sets%20of%20question%20papers%20were%20dispatched%20from%20SBI%20Hazaribagh%20to%20different%20centres.%20The%20ones%20that%20reached%20Oasis%20school%20centre%20had%20their%20seals%20broken.%20The%20staff%20there%20did%20not%20raise%20an%20alarm%20and%20thus%2C%20their%20role%20is%20established%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20official%20disclosed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBased%20on%20technical%20evidence%2C%20they%20had%20made%20searches%20in%20Learn%20and%20Play%20School%20in%20Patna%20where%20some%20burnt%20papers%20were%20recovered%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained%20adding%20that%20the%20case%20was%20later%20taken%20over%20by%20the%20Bihar%20Economic%20Offences%20Unit%20(EOU).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2021%2C%20the%20NTA%20disclosed%20that%20the%20code%20matched%20the%20papers%20found%20in%20Oasis%20school%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20principal%20of%20the%20school%2C%20Dr%20Ehsanul%20Haque%2C%20was%20also%20the%20district%20coordinator%20for%20the%20NEET-UG%20exam%20in%20Hazaribagh%20and%20vice-principal%20Imtiaz%20Alam%20was%20the%20centre%20coordinator.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%2C%20which%20is%20probing%20the%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20medical%20entrance%20exam%2C%20has%20registered%20several%20First%20Information%20Reports%20(FIRs)%20and%20made%20nearly%2060%20arrests%20so%20far.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NEET-UG%20exam%20-%20conducted%20by%20the%20National%20Testing%