lly%20have%20more%20packing%20space%20and%20are%20better%20for%20navigating%20uneven%20terrain%2C%20making%20them%20a%20solid%20option%20if%20you%20anticipate%20frequently%20navigating%20city%20subways%20and%20streets%20with%20your%20suitcase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExtra%20features%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20luggage%20brands%20aim%20to%20stand%20out%20by%20offering%20a%20fleet%20of%20special%20features.%20The%20features%20we%20find%20most%20useful%20are%20built-in%20combination%20locks%20and%20in-bag%20compression.%20Ejectable%20batteries%20are%20popular%20add-ons%2C%20but%20we%20find%20they're%20not%20often%20used%20and%20can%20be%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20pain%20to%20travel%20with%3A%20Most%20airlines%20do%20not%20allow%20these%20batteries%20to%20be%20checked%20into%20a%20plane's%20cargo%20hold.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Are%20the%20Prime%20Day%20furniture%20deals%20good%3F%5C%22%3EAre%20Prime%20Day%20luggage%20deals%20good%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPrime%20Day%20luggage%20deals%20typically%20echo%20savings%20you%20would%20find%20during%20major%20holidays%20like%20Memorial%20Day%2C%20Independence%20Day%2C%20and%20Black%20Friday.%20You'll%20be%20able%20to%20find%20savings%20on%20everything%20from%20travel%20backpacks%20to%20rolling%20luggage%20sets.%20Throughout%20the%20event%2C%20we'll%20be%20watching%20for%20new%20deals%20that%20go%20live%20and%20updating%20our%20articles%20with%20the%20best%20luggage%20discounts%20on%20Amazon%20and%20competing%20sites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EShopping%20for%20more%20great%20Amazon%20Prime%20Day%20deals%3F%20Check%20out%20our%20roundup%20of%20all%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fdeals%2Fbest-amazon-prime-day-deals-2024-7%5C%22%3Ebest%20deals%3C%2Fa%3E%20here%2C%20or%20browse%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-70721-20%26h%3D34bc15ccce60d2d0302c5e05187d6e06b596c2043ec7a1cbf7763