y's%20Herrsching%20at%20Lake%20Ammersee%20during%20the%20incident.%20Ms%20Kloos%20escaped%20the%20attack%20by%20scaling%20a%20wall%20and%20landing%20in%20her%20neighbour's%20house%2C%20from%20where%20she%20informed%20the%20cops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20power%20cables%20to%20the%20garage%20of%20Ian%20Cameron's%20house%2C%20where%20valuables%20were%20kept%2C%20had%20been%20purposefully%20cut%20off%2C%20according%20to%20CCTV%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20investigation%20suggests%20that%20this%20was%20a%20violent%20crime%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20police%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIan%20Cameron%20played%20a%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%26quot%3B%20role%20in%20the%20designing%20of%20iconic%20Rolls-Royce%20vehicles%20like%20the%20Ghost%2C%20Phantom%2C%20and%203%20Series.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIan%20Cameron%20undertook%20the%20role%20of%20leading%20the%20Rolls-Royce%20design%20team%20after%20BMW%20acquired%20Rolls-Royce's%20automotive%20business%20in%201998.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20deeply%20shocked%20and%20saddened%20by%20the%20news%20about%20our%20former%20Rolls-Royce%20designer.%20Our%20thoughts%20are%20with%20his%20family%20and%20friends%20during%20these%20difficult%20hours%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20BMW%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Automotive%20News.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIan%20played%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20shaping%20Rolls-Royce%20from%20when%20it%20was%20first%20acquired%20by%20BMW%20Group%20and%20moved%20to%20its%20home%20at%20Goodwood%2C%20West%20Sussex.%20During%20Ian's%20tenure%2C%20he%20led%20the%20design%20team%20for%20all%20Phantom%20family%20and%20Ghost%20models%2C%20creating%20thoroughly%20contemporary%20motor%20cars%20that%20remained%20sympathetic%20to%20the%20marque's%20design%20lineage%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20automaker%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suspect's%20height%20is%20estimated%20to%20be%20between%20180%20and%20190%20cm%20(5%20ft%209%20in%20to%206%20ft%202%20in).%20He%20is%20wearing%20light-c