%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIn%20exercise%20of%20the%20powers%20conferred%20by%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%2C%20Hon'ble%20President%2C%20after%20consultation%20with%20Hon'ble%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%2C%20is%20pleased%20to%20appoint%20the%20following%20as%3Cbr%3E%5CnSupreme%20Court%20Judges%3A-%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FOWQ9iGIooG%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FOWQ9iGIooG%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Arjun%20Ram%20Meghwal%20(%40arjunrammeghwal)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Farjunrammeghwal%2Fstatus%2F1813115139920425067%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2016%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20N%20Kotiswar%20Singh%C2%A0is%20the%20first%20judge%20from%20Manipur%20to%20be%20elevated%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20He%20is%20currently%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20Ladakh.%20Justice%20Singh%20is%20the%20son%20of%20Manipur's%20first%20Advocate%20General%20N%20Ibotombi%20Singh.%20An%20alumnus%20of%20Kirori%20Mal%20College%20and%20Campus%20Law%20Centre%2C%20Delhi%20University%2C%20he%20started%20is%20career%20as%20an%20advocate%20in%201986.%20He%20has%20also%20served%20as%20Manipur%20Advocate%20General%20before%20he%20became%20a%20judge.%20He%20has%20served%20in%20Gauhati%20High%20Court%20and%20Manipur%20High%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Mahadevan%20is%20currently%20the%20acting%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20Madras%20High%20Court.%20Born%20in%20Chennai%2C%20Justice%20Mahadevan%20is%20an%20alumnus%20of%20Madras%20Law%20College.%20As%20a%20lawyer%2C%20he%20has%20appeared%20in%20over%209%2C000%20cases%20and%20has%20also%20served%20as%20Additional%20Government%20Pleader%20(taxes)%20for%20the%20Government%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Additional%20Central%20Government%20Standing%20Counsel%20and%20Senior%20Panel%20Counsel%20for%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20at%20Madras%20High%20Court.%20He%20was%20elevated%20as%20a%