old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20met%20at%20Yale%20Law%20School%20and%20married%20in%20Kentucky%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20had%20two%20ceremonies%20-%20a%20traditional%20wedding%20ceremony%20and%20a%20separate%20Hindu%20ceremony%20conducted%20by%20a%20Hindu%20priest%2C%20honouring%20Usha's%20Hindu%20heritage.%20They%20have%20three%20children%20-%20Ewan%2C%206%2C%20Vivek%2C%204%2C%20and%20Mirabel%2C%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsha%2C%20reflecting%20on%20her%20upbringing%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Breligious%20household%26quot%3B%2C%20attributed%20her%20support%20for%20Vance's%20religious%20journey%20to%20her%20parents'%20influence.%20%26quot%3BMy%20parents%20are%20Hindu%20and%20that's%20one%20of%20the%20things%20that%20made%20them%20such%20good%20parents%20and%20good%20people.%20And%20I%20have%20seen%20the%20power%20of%20that%20in%20my%20own%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Usha.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20knew%20that%20JD%20was%20searching%20for%20something.%20This%20just%20felt%20right%20for%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20parents'%20Hindu%20faith%20made%20them%20great%20parents%E2%80%9D%20-%20Usha%20Vance%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnShe's%20a%20Hindu%20%26amp%3B%20was%20supportive%20of%20her%20husband's%20rediscovery%20of%20his%20own%20faith%20(One%20of%20her%20sons%20is%20named%20Vivek%20too%20%3F%3F%3F%3F)%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnVance%2C%20anti-war%20%26amp%3B%20Trump's%20VP%2C%20so%20far%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20net%20positive%20for%20India%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FKtbOUNT9ba%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FKtbOUNT9ba%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Alexei%20Arora%20(%40AlexeiArora)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAlexeiArora%2Fstatus%2F1812939370523160971%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2015%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%