n%208%2C000%20square-feet%20area.%20Every%20month%2C%20he%20harvests%20up%20to%20800%20kg%20of%20leafy%20greens%2C%20achieving%20five%20times%20the%20yield%20compared%20to%20conventional%20farming%20while%20using%20fewer%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20possible%20due%20to%20the%20protected%20cultivation%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F336600%2Ftech-nursery-hydroponics-aeroponics-farming-ratlam-brothers-arbind-ravindra-dhakad%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esystem%20of%20hydroponics%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhere%20crops%20are%20grown%20without%20soil!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20many%20soil%20borne%20diseases%20such%20as%20fungal%20and%20bacterial%20infections%20that%20affect%20crop%20yield.%20You%20cannot%20eliminate%20microorganisms%20and%20parasites%20like%20nematodes%20from%20the%20soil.%20So%2C%20I%20thought%20of%20eliminating%20soil%20itself%20as%20a%20medium%20altogether.%20I%20turned%20to%20hydroponics%2C%20which%20eliminates%20this%20worry%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPritpal%20now%20grows%20exotic%20leafy%20greens%20such%20as%20Italian%20basil%2C%20baby%20spinach%2C%20three%20to%20four%20kinds%20of%20lettuces%2C%20vine%20crops%20like%20red%20and%20yellow%20capsicum%20and%20seedless%20cucumbers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20grows%20these%20crops%20in%202.5%20acres%20of%20land%20comprising%20multiple%20types%20of%20protected%20environment%20structures%2C%20including%20an%20indoor%20vertical%20farm%2C%20a%20temperature-controlled%20polyhouse%2C%20a%20naturally-ventilated%20polyhouse%2C%20and%20indoor%20and%20outdoor%20hydroponics%20setups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FPritpal-4-1721052314.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pritpal%20gro