0in%20Sindhudurg%20district%2C%20first%20tried%20QR%20codes%2C%20bar%20codes%20and%20other%20methods%20to%20ensure%20authenticity.%20When%20middlemen%20found%20a%20way%20to%20tamper%20with%20these%20too%2C%20the%20Devgad%20Taluka%20Mango%20Grower%E2%80%99s%20Co-operative%20Society%20Limited%20found%20a%20unique%20way%20to%20protect%20their%20mangoes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20patented%20technology%20involves%20a%20tamper-proof%20sticker%20which%20cannot%20be%20replicated%20and%20ensures%20complete%20transparency%20and%20traceability.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20what%20it%20is%20and%20how%20it%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20makes%20the%20Devgad%20Hapus%20unique%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormed%20in%201987%2C%20the%20Devgad%20Taluka%20Mango%20Grower%E2%80%99s%20Co-operative%20Society%20has%20over%20900%20farmers%2C%20while%20the%20entire%20taluka%20has%202%2C000%20farmers.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20initially%20formed%20to%20bring%20small%20farmers%20together%20and%20help%20them%20take%20their%20produce%20to%20the%20market%20directly%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Omkar%20Sapre%2C%20the%20board%20member%20and%20advisor%20of%20the%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201068px)%20100vw%2C%201068px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdevgad4-1720776350.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221068%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Devgad%20Taluka%20Mango%20Grower%E2%80%99s%20Co-operative%20Society%20Limited%20have%20found%20a%20unique%20way%20to%20protect%20their%20mangoes%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdevgad4-1720776350.jpeg%201068w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdevgad4-1720776350-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdevgad4-1720776350-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdevgad4-1720776350-768x512.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdevgad4-1720776350-150x100.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356710%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22712%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDevgad%20Taluka%20Mango%20Grower%E2%80%99s%20Co-operative%20Society%20Limited%20have%20found%20a%20unique%20way%20to%20protect%20their%20mangoes%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20selling%20online%2C%20especially%20post%20COVID-19%2C%20which%20allowed%20us%20to%20reach%20customers%20directly.%20When%20you%20visit%20markets%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20you%20see%20many%20people%20selling%20the%20Devgad%20variety.%20Either%20they%20mix%20cheaper%20varieties%20with%20the%20original%20ones%20or%20just%20add%20stickers%20stating%20that%20it%20is%20from%20Devgad.%20To%20combat%20this%2C%20we%20applied%20for%20a%20GI%20tag%2C%20which%20we%20received%20in%202018%2C%E2%80%9D%20Omkar%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20GI%20tag%20is%20meant%20to%20protect%20the%20intellectual%20property%20of%20the%20producer%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20the%20farmer%2C%20and%20the%20place%20of%20origin%2C%20Devgad.%20It%20is%20additionally%20meant%20to%20benefit%2C%20enforce%20quality%20and%20prevent%20adulteration.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20lower%20quality%20mangoes%20which%20were%20being%20sold%20under%20the%20name%20of%20Devgad%20Hapus%20affected%20the%20Devgad%20brand.%20We%20wanted%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F349604%2Fhow-to-grow-japanese-mango-miyazaki-at-home-in-odisha-engineer-garden-with-rare-flower-fruit-plants-1000-petal-lotus%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eestablish%20the%20source%20and%20quality%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20tried%20barcode%20printing%2C%20edible%20ink%2C%20magnetic%20patterns%20and%20several%20other%20methods.%20They%20were%20all%20getting%20replicated%20by%20fakes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20one%20needs%20to%20understand%20is%20that%20the%20Devgad%20mango%20has%20a%20unique%20flavour%20due%20to%20the%20topography%20of%20the%20region.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDevgad%20has%20hard%20laterite%20rocks%2C%20which%20gives%20the%20fruits%20a%20splendid%20aroma.%20The%20high%20altitude%20gives%20it%20its%20unique%20taste%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Omkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESantosh%20Patkar%2C%20a%20farmer%2C%20states%20that%20what%20differentiates%20the%20Devgad%20variety%20from%20the%20ones%20found%20in%20Ratnagiri%20and%20other%20regions%20is%20its%20taste%2C%20colour%2C%20thin%20skin%2C%20and%20minimal%20fibre%20percentage.%20Speaking%20about%20the%20identity%20crisis%2C%20he%20shares%20that%20people%20are%20selling%20fake%20Devgad%20mangoes%20even%20after%20their%20production%20is%20over%20for%20the%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20are%20selling%20mangoes%20from%20Karnataka%20and%20calling%20it%20Devgad%20Hapus.%20Retailers%20and%20online%20stores%20are%20duping%20people%20while%20charging%20a%20bomb.%20Due%20to%20this%2C%20our%20rate%20and%20value%20is%20also%20coming%20down%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20it%20works%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20mentioned%20earlier%2C%20the%20problem%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F260907%2Findia-gi-tag-konkan-alphonso-mango-farmers-income%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EQR%20codes%20or%20bar%20codes%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20that%20it%20can%20be%20copied.%20Prashant%20Yadav%2C%20an%20engineer%20and%20founder%20of%20Sun%20Solutions%2C%20developed%20the%20patented%20technology.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimply%20put%2C%20the%20unique%20code%20of%20each%20product%20is%20divided%20into%20two%20parts%2C%20one%20ab