%20works%20seamlessly%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Suneet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20nearly%2010%20months%20a%20year%2C%20the%20couple%20claims%20to%20use%20zero%20energy%20from%20the%20grid.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20consume%20some%20energy%20from%20the%20grid%20for%20about%20two%20months%20in%20the%20summer%20when%20we%20have%20to%20run%20the%20air%20conditioner%20by%20the%20night.%20Sometimes%2C%20there%20isn%E2%80%99t%20enough%20generation%20in%20the%20day%20to%20run%20the%20AC%20at%20all%20hours%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20we%20end%20up%20having%20Rs%201%2C500-Rs%202%2C000%20bills%20in%20those%20months%2C%20of%20which%20the%20fixed%20metre%20charge%20is%20about%20Rs%20500%20to%20700%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20setup%20cost%20the%20couple%20Rs%2015%20lakh%20and%20they%20believe%20they%20would%20get%20the%20return%20on%20investment%20within%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20limitations%20of%20the%20entire%20grid-backed%20setup%2C%20Shilpa%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9COver%20the%20years%2C%20we%20developed%20a%20habit%20of%20running%20the%20washing%20machine%2C%20the%20mixer%2C%20water%20pumps%20only%20in%20the%20solar%20hours%20between%2010am%20to%205pm%20or%20it%20will%20lead%20to%20storage%20exhaustion.%20We%20run%20four%20ACs%20in%20the%20day%20and%20only%20two%20at%20night.%20You%20require%20this%20kind%20of%20discipline.%20But%20these%20are%20all%20matters%20of%20choice.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsolar-2-1720701386.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20couple%20harness%20solar%20energy%20to%20use%20energy%20consuming%20appliances%20like%20induction%2C%20microwave%2C%20washing%20machine.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F0