er%20two%20versions%20of%20their%20deterrent%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20our%20main%20products%20is%20a%20solar-powered%20auto%20light%2C%20effective%20against%20various%20wild%20animals%20such%20as%20elephants%2C%20wild%20boars%2C%20and%20tigers.%20It%20is%20called%20Parabraksh.%20This%20product%20operates%20automatically%2C%20flashing%20in%20different%20patterns%20throughout%20the%20night%2C%20creating%20the%20illusion%20of%20another%20animal%20in%20the%20area%2C%20which%20deters%20these%20animals%20from%20entering%20the%20fields%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20solar-powered%20autonomous%20light%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20operates%20automatically%2C%20switching%20on%20at%20sunset%20and%20flashing%20in%20various%20patterns%20throughout%20the%20night%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20LED%20light%20itself%20isn%E2%80%99t%20inherently%20threatening.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20way%20the%20system%20is%20designed%20to%20be%20perceived%20by%20the%20animals%20that%20makes%20it%20effective.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20significant%20product%20that%20the%20company%20offers%20is%20the%20bioplastic%20scare%20system%2C%20which%20they%20call%20Kaapikat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-8-1720534857.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22All%20the%20products%20provided%20by%20the%20startup%20are%20non-invasive%20and%20do%20not%20harm%20the%20animals.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-8-1720534857.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-8-1720534857-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%